{
  "texts": [
    "Then we use Llama2-13B-Chat to generate the answers according to the input prompt.",
    "The results are recorded in Figure 11.",
    "TopFrom this figure, we can see that the answering accuracy drops by 0.6% on TriviaQA, 0.2% on NQ and 0.1% on PopQA respectively, when the data-imbalance-aware bi-label learning algorithm is excluded.",
    "The drops on the NQ and PopQA are not significant because of the labels in these two datasets is highly noisy and the imbalance ratio is undetermined.This result demonstrates that our approach can effectively address data imbalance and improve the performance of black-box RAG.",
    "Effect of Bi-faceted Self-Knowledge RecognizerTo investigate the effect of the bi-faceted self-knowledge recognizer, we conduct an ablation study on it."
